  <h2>Marketing</h2>
  <p>
    Amplify your voice by translating your brand to an infinite array of print, digital, and video
    campaigns that can grow with you and remain authentic in a multitude of touchpoints.
  </p>

  <div class="cardgrid-container">
    <div class="card-noshadow two-column">
      <div class="resource-text">
        <h3 class="resource-title">ABB</h3>
        <a href="#" aria-disabled="true">Writing in progress&nbsp;&#128274;</a>
